OL,3,C29% of UK adults hit by Royal Mail
OL,4,Cdelays over Christmas, warns Citizens
OL,5,CAdvice
OL,7,FAn estimated 16 million people ` or
OL,8,F29% of UK adults ` experienced post
OL,9,Fdelays with Royal Mail over Christmas,
OL,10,FCitizens Advice has said.
OL,12,FThe figure, which applies to letters
OL,13,Fand cards but not parcels, is a 50%
OL,14,Fincrease on December 2024, up from
OL,15,F10.7 million people, the charity found.
OL,17,FSome 5.7 million people missed vital
OL,18,Fletters about health appointments,
OL,19,Ffines, benefit decisions and legal
OL,20,Fdocuments, it warned.
