OL,3,C29% of UK adults hit by Royal Mail
OL,4,Cdelays over Christmas, warns Citizens
OL,5,CAdvice
OL,7,FAside from 2022, when Royal Mail took
OL,8,Fstrike action, the charity's annual
OL,9,Fresearch found the number of people
OL,10,Fexperiencing these issues over the
OL,11,Ffestive period was the highest in five
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FCitizens Advice, the statutory
OL,15,Fwatchdog for post, said not enough was
OL,16,Fbeing done to prioritise consumers who
OL,17,Fhad "no choice but to put up with
OL,18,Fdelivery delays and service cuts,
OL,19,Fdespite increasing stamp prices".
