OL,3,C29% of UK adults hit by Royal Mail
OL,4,Cdelays over Christmas, warns Citizens
OL,5,CAdvice
OL,7,FAlmost a quarter of those who
OL,8,Fexperienced post delays (22%) said
OL,9,Fthey were left feeling anxious or
OL,10,Fdistressed about benefits, bills,
OL,11,Flosing money and missing other
OL,12,Ffinancial information.
OL,14,FThe cost of a 1st class stamp, now
OL,15,F#1,70, has more than doubled since
OL,16,F2020 despite Royal Mail failing to
OL,17,Fmeet a 1st class annual delivery
OL,18,Ftarget since 2017 or a 2nd class
OL,19,Ftarget since 2020.
