OL,3,C29% of UK adults hit by Royal Mail
OL,4,Cdelays over Christmas, warns Citizens
OL,5,CAdvice
OL,7,FIn July last year, regulator Ofcom
OL,8,Fannounced cuts to Royal Mail's 2nd
OL,9,Fclass delivery days alongside lower
OL,10,Fdelivery targets as part of the review
OL,11,Fof the Universal Service Obligation
OL,12,F(USO).
OL,14,FThe company now only has to deliver
OL,15,F2nd class post every other weekday,
OL,16,Finstead of six days a week, with these
OL,17,Fchanges set to be rolled out
OL,18,Fnationwide this year.
