OL,3,C29% of UK adults hit by Royal Mail
OL,4,Cdelays over Christmas, warns Citizens
OL,5,CAdvice
OL,7,FAnne Pardoe, head of policy at
OL,8,FCitizens Advice, said: "We're afraid
OL,9,Fthere's no light at the end of the
OL,10,Ftunnel for consumers struggling with
OL,11,FRoyal Mail's persistent delivery
OL,12,Ffailures. When people have no other
OL,13,Fpostal provider to choose from, the
OL,14,Fsheer volume of delays is simply
OL,15,Funacceptable.
OL,17,F"The company's dreadful festive slump
OL,18,Fis about much more than late Christmas
OL,19,Fcards. People are left distressed
OL,20,Fafter missing health appointments,
OL,21,Ffines and benefit decisions.
