OL,3,C29% of UK adults hit by Royal Mail
OL,4,Cdelays over Christmas, warns Citizens
OL,5,CAdvice
OL,7,F"This is a worrying trend, and with
OL,8,Fcuts to delivery days looming, Ofcom
OL,9,Fmust start cracking down even harder
OL,10,Fon missed targets before things go
OL,11,Ffrom bad to worse. Any future stamp
OL,12,Fprice increases should be conditional
OL,13,Fon Royal Mail meeting these targets."
OL,15,FA Royal Mail spokesman said:
OL,16,F"Independent data shows that more than
OL,17,F99% of items posted by the last
OL,18,Frecommended dates arrived in time for
OL,19,FChristmas.
