OL,7,F"Last year, we modernised the
OL,8,Fobligations imposed on Royal Mail, to
OL,9,Freflect what people need, put the
OL,10,Fservice on a more sustainable footing,
OL,11,Fand enable the company to invest more
OL,12,Fin improving its delivery performance.
OL,14,F"Royal Mail must now play its part by
OL,15,Fimplementing this effectively and
OL,16,Fimproving its reliability."
